column5: Hey guys!  I'm a newbie to this site. Looks great so far. Looking forward to being apart of the community. Even though I live in Manitoba I do a good portion of my fishing in NW Ontario. Gotta Love sunset country!  A buddy and myself filmed/edited this video last week. I'd love to hear some feedback!  www.youtube.com/watch?v=lEPmYOI7EbM&feature=relmfu  -Jay Siemens
